` processes real-time clock logic by calling the `RTC_MS` function block and supports DST and time offset calculations. The final outputs include the updated time value, local time value, DST flag, and milliseconds value. This function block is suitable for applications requiring precise time management and timezone adjustments.", "name": "RTC_2"}